title: Ukrainian Coder's New Programming Language: One Big Data Structure
author: David Cassel
description: Inspired by languages like Forth, APL, Uiua, and PostScript, the nameless programming language is an experiment in tacit programming.
cntitle: 乌克兰程序员的新编程语言：一个大型数据结构
cndescription: 受 Forth、APL、Uiua 和 PostScript 等语言的启发，无名编程语言是对默示编程的一次实验。
